PolyForm Noncommercial License 1.0.0

Noncommercial Use

Users of the software may use the software for any purpose that is not a
Commercial Use.

"Commercial Use" means use:
1.  by a business, similar organization, or individual, that is not an academic
    institution or a Tax-Exempt Organization; AND
2.  for a commercial purpose, such as to increase profit or generate revenue.

"Tax-Exempt Organization" means any entity that has tax-exempt status in the
jurisdiction where it is organized, such as a section 501(c)(3) organization in
the United States. 

